name: YARD OWLS Wave 2) "SHARON le Vampyr"
description:
For OCTOBER the YARD OWLS are getting a NOIR treatement.
Some will be spooky, some will be Hollywood Glamour.

All will be mysterious and rare! 

There will be 5 of each character -- 15 characters in all. 
That's it only 75 cards in Wave 2.

On 10/15 I'll burn all that remains from the September set - which was "YARD OWLS in 3D." If you want to collect these, grab them now, on Secondary they will go up quick. (wink)


ABOUT THIS OWL:

SHARON : While normally she would be telling you how to do what you do, and why it's all wrong ... This month she wants to get close to you ... CLOSE enough to do some 'necking' and YES she WOULD like to DRINK your manager, actually! Which OWL will get the NOIR treatment for tomorrow????

EDITION 5/5 for only 1 TEZ Collect them All!

YARD OWLS - Noir Collection : October 2021 : YO13.2
HP LoveBux
